data.description: (OPEN SAT, 4/27-1-4pm). BEAUTIFUL & WELL-MAINTAINED HOME NESTLED ON AN APPROX .84 ACRE LOT IN THE ESTABLISHED GREAT NECK NEIGHBORHOOD OF LAUREL COVE. IN ADDITION TO THE GRACIOUS LIVING, DINING & FAMILY ROOMS, THIS HOME OFFERS A WONDERFUL GREAT ROOM WITH REAR WALL OF WINDOWS FOR NATURAL SUNLIGHT THAT OPENS TO THE PRIVATE BACKYARD & POOL AREA FOR EASY ENTERTAINING. CHEF’S KITCHEN W/ CUSTOM ISLAND. TWO EN SUITE PRIMARY BEDROOMS.  ADDITIONAL UPDATES INCLUDE; APPROX 1,000 sq ft ADDITION (2006), ROOF (2016), POOL INSTALLED (2017), FLOORS REFINISHED/KITCHEN UPDATED/APPLIANCES (2019), DOWNSTAIRS GAS HVAC (2021), UPSTAIRS HALL BATH (2022), REMODELED LG PRIMARY BATH (2022), POOL SALT CELL & PUMP (2022), TANKLESS GAS WATER HEATER (2022), ENLARGED LAUNDRY/STORAGE (2022) & POOL LINER (2023). OVERSIZED ATTACHED 2 CAR GARAGE W/ SHELVING & WORK BENCH.  DETACHED GARAGE/WORKSHOP AT REAR OF PROPERTY-"AS IS".  SPEAKER SYSTEM NOT CONNECTED TO RECEIVER-"AS IS". CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT W/ SUPERIOR TERMITE.
